description:
The #Danube is the longest #River in the EU, carving its path through the Central European mountain ranges, and visiting a total of 10 countries along the way. 

For more videos about the great rivers of our planet, check out this playlist:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL1SsGP17-kZXwnc3b8ABu9fy_uWDlZz0j
